Package tellosimulator.command

Class CommandHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • tellosimulator.command.CommandHandler
  • public class CommandHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Splits, validates and redirects incoming commands from the CommandConnection to the appropriate methods in the DroneController.
